CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 12, 1941, pg. 8, reads: "Pretty Jackson-Cralle Nuptials Bring Socialites Together In Festive Affair - The Jackson-Cralle nuptials last Saturday evening proved one of smoke town's smartest affairs... the bride and groom center... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Bride Jean Bernie Jackson Cralle wearing long sleeved gown with train, and groom Paul Cralle, standing in Loendi Club
